     */
    @java.lang.SuppressWarnings(&quot;all&quot;)
    public void setSomething(final String something) {
        this.something = something;
    }
    
    [‚Ä¶]
}
```

&#185; This appears to actually have been implemented in PR [#2008](https://github.com/projectlombok/lombok/pull/2008), which was part of [v1.18.6](https://projectlombok.org/changelog)

